There is yet no automated tests. Here some manual:

- Generate a new rpm and install it:
    $ tools/make_rpm
    $ sudo yum install ~/rpmbuild/RPMS/noarch/lpf-0-2.b7cd782.fc18.noarch.rpm

- Verify the help output:
    $ lpf -h

- Remove all target and lpf packages:
    $ sudo rpm -e spotify-client msttcore-fonts
    $ sudo rpm -e lpf-msttcore-fonts lpf-spotify-client
    error: package lpf-msttcore-fonts is not installed
    error: package lpf-spotify-client is not installed

- Build lpf-msttcore-fonts:
    cd examples/msttcore-fonts/
    cp * ~/rpmbuild/SOURCES/
    rpmbuild -ba lpf-msttcore-fonts.spec
    $ sudo rpm -U --force ~/rpmbuild/RPMS/noarch/lpf-msttcore-fonts-2.2-1.fc18.noarch.rpm


- Build lpf-spotify-client
    cd examples/spotify-client/
    cp * ~/rpmbuild/SOURCES/
    rpmbuild -bb lpf-spotify-client.spec
    sudo rpm -U --force ~/rpmbuild/RPMS/noarch/lpf-spotify-client-0.9.0.133.gd18ed58.259-1.fc18.noarch.rpm

- Test lpf list

    $ lpf list
    spotify-client
    msttcore-fonts

- Check lpf state:

    $ lpf state
    spotify-client       approve-wait   0.9.0.133.gd18ed58.259-2.fc18
    msttcore-fonts       approve-wait   2.2-1

- Check that there are three applications available in gnome: lpf,
  lpf-spotify-client, lpf-msttcore-fonts with correct factory icon

- Check approve followed by 'Cancel':

    $ lpf approve spotify-client
    $ lpf state
    spotify-client                     not-approved   0.9.0.133.gd18ed58.259-2.fc18
    msttcore-fonts                     approve-wait   2.2-1

- Check non-gui update of just spotify-client:

    $ DISPLAY= lpf update spotify-client
    ::::::::::::::
    /usr/share/lpf/packages/spotify-client/eula/eula.txt
    ::::::::::::::
    Copyright (c) 2002-2006, Marc Prud'hommeaux <mwp1@cornell.edu>
    All rights reserved.

    ...

    Do you accept these license terms [n] y
    spotify-client: downloading sources
    spotify-client: installing build dependencies
    spotify-client: building
    spotify-client: storing results
    spotify-client: build completed
    Install spotify-client-0.9.0.133.gd18ed58.259-2.fc18.i686.rpm (Yes/no) [y] ? y

    spotify-client: installing /var/lib/lpf/rpms/spotify-client/spotify-client-0.9.0.133.gd18ed58.259-2.fc18.i686.rpm.

    $ lpf state
    spotify-client     OK             0.9.0.133.gd18ed58.259-2.fc18
    msttcore-fonts     approve-wait   2.2-1

- Check corresponding GUI update of lpf-msttcore-fonts: click on the lpf-msttcore-fonts icon

- Check that repeated GUI update displays correct "Nothing to update" message.

- Check that lpf log displays last log from msttcore-fonts.

